{"tid":2488932,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★酒樓集團強制員工本月底前打疫苗 違者將被停工","createTime":"2021-04-14T14:41:42.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T14:46:44.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a5a1f806fcf00c2d5e8850305f89340ddb11ee87","tid":2488932,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T14:41:42.000Z","msg":"有連鎖酒樓集團今(14日)被指，要求所有食肆員工於本月26日前，必須完成第一針新冠疫苗接種，否則於本月29日起停工。<br />\n<br />\n有連鎖酒樓集團今發出內部通告，指因應政府近日公佈以接種疫苗的「疫苗氣泡」前提下，可調整及放寬下一輪社交距離措施，故要求所有食肆員工在本月26日前，必須完成第一針疫苗接種，並把接種紀錄經手機通訊軟件傳到人力資源部存檔，否則有關員工將由本月29日起安排停工。通告指，若員工持醫生證明信，列明身體狀況不宜打針，則可待政府公佈可否獲豁免。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%80%A3%E9%8E%96%E9%85%92%E6%A8%93%E9%9B%86%E5%9C%98%E9%80%BC%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E6%9C%AC%E6%9C%88%E5%BA%95%E5%89%8D%E6%89%93%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97-%E9%81%95%E8%80%85%E5%B0%87%E8%A2%AB%E5%81%9C%E5%B7%A5-100406693.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E9%2580%25A3%25E9%258E%2596%25E9%2585%2592%25E6%25A8%2593%25E9%259B%2586%25E5%259C%2598%25E9%2580%25BC%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%25BA%2595%25E5%2589%258D%25E6%2589%2593%25E7%2596%25AB%25E8%258B%2597-%25E9%2581%2595%25E8%2580%2585%25E5%25B0%2587%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2581%259C%25E5%25B7%25A5-100406693.html&d=t2%2FAN0mLur8%2Bj%2B1TvbkzvrTr7UizNwCuyTydxCoZ6r4%3D&h=02206c56\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%80%A3%E9%8E%96%E9%85%92%E6%A8%93%E9%9B%86%E5%9C%98%E9%80%BC%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E6%9C%AC%E6%9C%88%E5%BA%95%E5%89%8D%E6%89%93%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97-%E9%81%95%E8%80%85%E5%B0%87%E8%A2%AB%E5%81%9C%E5%B7%A5-100406693.html</a>"},{"pid":"43d24eefe73b06c422b73dace97703185e2f123a","tid":2488932,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T14:41:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /